SECTION 1. SHORT TITLE. This Act shall be known and may be cited as the General Appropriations Act of 2025.

“Capital project number” means the official number of the capital project, as assigned by the responsible organization.

The department of transportation is authorized to issue airport revenue bonds for airport capital improvement program projects authorized in part II and listed in part IV of this Act and designated to be financed by revenue bond funds or by general obligation bond funds.
